rstLineIndent="2" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify">This enactment amends the <I>Excise Tax Act</I> to eliminate the goods and services tax on the sale, for the benefit of veterans, of Remembrance Day poppies and poppy wreaths.</Para></Block></Bill_Part><Bill_Part Part_Type="MainText" CountLines="Yes" RunningHead_E="Excise Tax (no GST on poppies or poppy wreathes)"><Block Align="Yes"><Para Style="MainText_DocNo">402405</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="Session_Reign">2nd Session, 40th Parliament,</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="Session_Reign">57-58 Elizabeth II, 2009</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="MainBillOrigin">house of commons of canada</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Bold="Yes" Style="MAIN@BillNo_Title">BILL C-480</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="MAIN@ti;04">An Act to amend the Excise Tax Act (no GST on poppies or poppy wreaths)</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><MarginalNote>R.S., c. E-15<br/></MarginalNote><Para LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify">Her Majesty, with the advice and consent of the Senate and House of Commons of Canada, enacts as follows:</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Bold="Yes"><B>1.</B> Schedule VI of the <I>Excise Tax Act</I> is amended by adding the following after <keep>Part X:</keep></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes" KeepWith="Next"><Para TopMargin="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="OFF" TextAlign="Center"><change>PART XI </change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes" KeepWith="Next"><!--Heading:MEMORIAL SYMBOLS--><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="OFF" TextAlign="Center"><change>MEMORIAL SYMBOLS</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change